<ul><li>Add information and practices for starting a club, joining the network, hosting an event (a few sources are listed under <a href="http://dandelion.liquidfridge.co.za/notes/drafts/resources" rel="nofollow">Resources</a>). Perhaps divide the page into 2 parts: an introduction with call to action(s), and an expanded section for deeper reading/FAQ things.</li>
