  <h1 class="book-heading">Get Involved</h1>
  <div class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden"><div class="field__items"><div class="field__item even"><h2>How to get involved</h2>

<p>If the ideas presented here hit you square in the feels, and you have a suggestion for improving the concept, get in touch with us.</p>

